  "title": "Two pilots report a TCAS&#8217; detection of a UFO [2015]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/05/30/two-pilots-report-a-tcass-detection-of-a-ufo-2015/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-3M",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>MAY 9th, 2015.</b> At 18h04pm, two pilots from the same brazilian air company reported an unidentified flying object &#8211; detected by the TCAS (Traffic Collision Avoidance System) of their plane &#8211; moving at a speed approximately of 450 km/h and heading Northeast from the State of Rio de Janeiro&#8217;s airspace. Still according to the report, the event lasted five minutes and it was only detected by the TCAS. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.732. &#8220;<span class=\"s1\"><i>Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni)</i></span>&#8220;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
